devdoc.details: Multisig Wallet Smart Contract where multiple signatures/approvals  are needed for an outgoing transfer to take place. Anyone can deposit funds.  As soon as we want to spend funds, it requires the specified number of approvals.

approve(uint256).details: A method to approve a transfer by an owner.

deposit().details: A method to make a deposit.

getBalance().details: A method that create an instance of the Transfer struct and push it into the transferRequests array function createTransfer(uint _amount, address payable _receiver) public onlyOwners{ emit TransferRequestCreated(transferRequests.length, _amount, msg.sender, _receiver);         transferRequests.push(Transfer(_amount, _receiver, 0, false, transferRequests.length)); } /**A method to get the sender's balance.

withdraw(uint256).details: A method to make a withdrawal only if there is sufficient balance.
